name: The First Seduction
overview:
The First Seduction provides men with the knowledge needed to become more attractive to the opposite sex.

Resources given to men include, original informative articles on dating & attraction, freely distributed eBooks on subjects such texting & seduction, & original videos distributed on platforms such as Youtube and Vimeo giving men answers to questions around self-confidence and more.

The company was launched to promote self-confidence in ones self & abilities so men can live a more fulfilled life. This is achieved through being live & active on all social networking sites including Facebook & Twitter where useful information is shared and a connection with viewers can be made.

Publishing useful content free of charge & monetizing through avenues such as useful product reviews is the central business model behind The First Seductions operations & we’ll be for the foreseeable future.
